        "created_at": "2016-11-06T08:36:36.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Haven\u2019t had a Roty at mature stage yet.<br>\nThe Danish importer was located close to Me once, and I tasted several of the early '00s at very young. Tough wines !<br>\nStill, I bought the 02 Charmes, and the even rarer Maziz (75 cases prod.). I hope to live and drink them at peak, -in the far future.</p>\n<p>Thanks for excellent note.<br>\n-S\u00f8ren.</p>",
